p>\n<p>\n<label for=\"T156_25\">Alignment:</label>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"T156_25\" name=\"Alignment\" value=\"Normal. No scoliosis or kyphosis\"/>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section data-section-name=\"Impression\">\n<header class=\"level1\">Impression</header>\n<p>\n<textarea id=\"T156_31\" name=\"Impression\">Normal examination. </textarea>\n</p>\n</section>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
